          </p>
          <p>
            Contact: <%= link_to "ovh.com", "https://www.ovh.com/fr/", target: '_blank', class: 'link' %>
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
    <p class="font-bold">2026 © <%= @sitename %> – All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
